                <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-12 col-xl-12">
                    <div id="about" class="tabcontent">
                        <h1 class="font-weight-bold mb-4">Best Family-Friendly Hotels in India for a Perfect Getaway | Book My Hotels</h1>

                        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded shadow-sm mb-4">
                            <p>
                                If your idea of romance involves sun-kissed beaches, candlelit dinners by the sea, and cozy stays with a touch of luxury — then India’s boutique beach hotels are calling your name. From the serene shores of Kerala to the vibrant beaches of Goa and the untouched beauty of the Andaman Islands, India offers an incredible mix of romantic seaside getaways.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                At <strong>Book My Hotels</strong>, we bring you some of the best boutique beach hotels in India, perfect for couples who want a peaceful, intimate, and unforgettable experience.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Hotel 1 -->
                        <div class="card mb-3 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">1. Ahilya by the Sea – Goa</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    Goa isn’t just about parties — it’s also one of India’s most romantic beach destinations. Ahilya by the Sea, located in Nerul, offers a peaceful escape with just a handful of elegant villas surrounded by gardens and sea views.
                                </p>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    The infinity pool overlooking the Arabian Sea and private balconies make it a top boutique hotel in Goa for couples.
                                </p>
                                <p class="card-text"><strong>Best for:</strong> Romantic sunset views, private dining, and quiet luxury.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Hotel 2 -->
                        <div class="card mb-3 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">2. Niraamaya Retreats Surya Samudra – Kovalam, Kerala</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    Nestled along the rocky coast of Kovalam, Niraamaya Retreats offers a perfect blend of Kerala’s traditional architecture and modern comfort.
                                </p>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    Private cottages with open-air bathrooms, a world-class spa, and oceanfront dining create the ultimate romantic beach retreat in South India.
                                </p>
                                <p class="card-text"><strong>Best for:</strong> Ayurvedic spa sessions, beach walks, and authentic Kerala seafood.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Hotel 3 -->
                        <div class="card mb-3 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">3. Radisson Blu Resort Temple Bay – Mahabalipuram, Tamil Nadu</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    Located on the Coromandel Coast, this resort offers stunning oceanfront villas, a meandering pool, and fine dining options.
                                </p>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    The combination of heritage and coastal charm makes it one of the best romantic resorts in South India.
                                </p>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    <strong>Best for:</strong> Couples who love culture and sea views — just steps away from Mahabalipuram’s UNESCO monuments.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Hotel 4 -->
                        <div class="card mb-3 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">4. Barefoot at Havelock – Andaman Islands</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    If you dream of escaping to a secluded island, Barefoot at Havelock is paradise. Set beside Radhanagar Beach — often rated among the best in Asia — this eco-luxury resort offers wooden cottages surrounded by tropical forests and turquoise water.
                                </p>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    <strong>Best for:</strong> Honeymooners seeking peace, scuba diving, and untouched nature.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Hotel 5 -->
                        <div class="card mb-3 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">5. Marbela Beach Resort – Morjim, Goa</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    For couples who love bohemian luxury, Marbela Beach Resort blends comfort with chic style. Stay in luxurious tents right on the beach, enjoy live music nights, and unwind under the stars.
                                </p>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    <strong>Best for:</strong> Trendy couples and beach lovers looking for vibrant yet cozy stays.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Why Choose -->
                        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded shadow-sm mt-5">
                            <h4 class="mb-3">Why Choose Book My Hotels for Your Romantic Beach Getaway?</h4>
                            <p>
                                At Book My Hotels, we handpick properties that combine comfort, beauty, and authenticity. Whether you’re planning a honeymoon, an anniversary trip, or a spontaneous weekend by the sea, our platform helps you find the best boutique beach hotels in India — with exclusive offers, verified reviews, and secure bookings.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                So, let the waves whisper romance into your next escape.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                Explore Book My Hotels and make your dream seaside getaway in India come true today.
                            </p>
                        </div>


                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
